kglobe.com/img/07e7/03/1c/1108863592_0:0:3072:1728_1280x0_80_0_0_2a110710cb1b0b0c7e3f8371f20bf945.jpg 1280w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/03/1c/1108863592_0:0:3072:1728_1920x0_80_0_0_a7376099ddc325bde115412083f0e5ba.jpg 1920w" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div></div><div class="media__copyright " data-nosnippet=""><div class="media__copyright-item m-copyright"> © Sputnik / 斯特林格</div></div></div></div><div class="article__messengers"><div class="flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label"></span></div><div class="flex-align_center"></div><div class="article__telegram-news flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label">订阅</span></div><div class="flex-align_center"><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/SputnikInt" title="国际的" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">国际的</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://telegram.me/sputniknewsindia" title="印度" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">印度</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/sputnik_africa" title="非洲" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">非洲</a></div></div></div><div class="article__announce-text">据莫斯科（人造卫星）网报道：根据该国数字化转型部的空袭数据，周六深夜，包括基辅在内的乌克兰多个地区发布了空袭警告。 </div></div><div class="article__body"><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">该部的在线地图显示，午夜过后不久，空袭警报在尼古拉耶夫、基洛沃格勒、切尔尼戈夫、第聂伯罗彼得罗夫斯克和基辅的乌克兰地区以及乌克兰控制的赫尔松地区部分地区响起。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">自 10 月 10 日（克里米亚大桥恐怖袭击发生两天后）以来，俄罗斯对乌克兰基础设施实施了精确打击。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">深夜，乌克兰首都基辅以及日托米尔和苏梅地区发布了空袭警报。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"> 2月，乌克兰电网运营商Ukrenergo负责人表示，俄罗斯空袭对乌克兰能源基础设施造成的直接破坏可能高达数亿美元，经济损失达数十亿。</div></div></div> ]]>;</description><pubDate> Sat, 27 May 2023 22:27:06 GMT</pubDate><guid ispermalink="false"> https://sputniknews.com/20230527/air-raid-sirens-go-off-in-several-regions-of-ukraine-including-kiev---authorities-1110644030.html</guid><link/> https://sputniknews.com/20230527/air-raid-sirens-go-off-in-several-regions-of-ukraine-including-kiev---authorities-1110644030.html<category>俄罗斯在乌克兰的特别行动</category><category>乌克兰</category><category>基辅</category><category>尼古拉耶夫</category><category>乌克兰能源公司</category></item><item><title><![CDATA[Putin Says Border Guards to Continue Protecting Russia’s Sovereignty Territorial Integrity]]></title><description><![CDATA[<div class="article__header"><div class="article__announce"><div class="media" data-media-tipe="ar16x9"><div class="media__size"><div class="photoview__open" data-photoview-group="1110643895" data-photoview-src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/1a/1110613082_0:0:3071:2048_1440x900_80_0_1_6829d2e48fc4c6f3cba132e55015736c.jpg?source-sid=rian_photo" data-photoview-image-id="1110613064" data-photoview-sharelink="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230527/putin-says-border-guards-to-continue-protecting-russias-sovereignty-territorial-integrity-1110643895.html?share-img=1110613064"><noindex><div class="photoview__open-info"> <span class="photoview__copyright">© Sputnik / Mikhail Klimentyev</span><span class="photoview__desc-text">俄罗斯总统弗拉基米尔·普京</span></div></noindex><img media-type="ar16x9" data-source-sid="rian_photo" alt="Russian President Vladimir Putin - Sputnik International, 1920, 27.05.2023" title="俄罗斯总统普京" src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/1a/1110613082_0:0:3071:1728_1920x0_80_0_0_c3f4ed5d43910254907e11a5b3160a7e.jpg" decoding="async" width="1920" height="1080" srcset="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/1a/1110613082_0:0:3071:1728_640x0_80_0_0_29b3db599a563b4f03f323a0148b097b.jpg 640w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/1a/1110613082_0:0:3071:1728_1280x0_80_0_0_ca27891e4a28737a0510d73ab62452dd.jpg 1280w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/1a/1110613082_0:0:3071:1728_1920x0_80_0_0_c3f4ed5d43910254907e11a5b3160a7e.jpg 1920w" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div></div><div class="media__copyright " data-nosnippet=""><div class="media__copyright-item m-copyright"> © Sputnik / Mikhail Klimentyev</div> / </div></div></div><div class="article__messengers"><div class="flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label"></span></div><div class="flex-align_center"></div><div class="article__telegram-news flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label">订阅</span></div><div class="flex-align_center"><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/SputnikInt" title="国际的" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">国际的</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://telegram.me/sputniknewsindia" title="印度" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">印度</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/sputnik_africa" title="非洲" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">非洲</a></div></div></div><div class="article__announce-text">据莫斯科（人造卫星）网报道：俄罗斯总统弗拉基米尔·普京在边防军日向退伍军人和现役军人表示祝贺，称俄罗斯边防军将继续保护国家的主权和领土完整，并将确保军用和民用货物运往新的组成实体俄罗斯。 </div></div><div class="article__body"><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"> <strong>“你们，战胜纳粹的胜利者一代的接班人和继承人，继续光荣地、有尊严地履行你们的职责，解决具有挑战性的优先任务，保卫国家边界，开展边境控制和海洋资源保护，为实施国际一体化项目和发展跨境合作、打击跨国犯罪和走私、防止转移和恐怖袭击做出重要贡献，”普京</strong>在周日的声明中说。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">俄罗斯总统感谢边防人员的服务，特别是那些参加乌克兰特别军事行动的人员。 </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="quote"><div class="article__quote"><div class="article__quote-text">普京说：“我相信，你将继续大公无私、勇敢高效地行动，称职有效地利用一切可用的资源和手段，捍卫俄罗斯的主权和领土完整以及我国人民的安全。” </div><div class="article__quote-info"><div class="elem-info"><div class="elem-info__share"><div class="share" data-id="1110643895" data-url="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230527/putin-says-border-guards-to-continue-protecting-russias-sovereignty-territorial-integrity-1110643895.html?share-block=1110643898" data-title="&quot;I am confident that you will continue to act selflessly, bravely and efficiently, and will competently and effectively use all available resources and means to protect the sovereignty and territorial integrity of Russia and the security of our people,&quot; Putin said. "></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">总统说，俄罗斯边防部队必须与联邦安全局、武装部队和俄罗斯联邦国民警卫队的其他单位以及地方政府机构密切合作。 </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="quote"><div class="article__quote"><div class="article__quote-text"> “......至关重要的是确保军用和民用车辆和货物，包括食品、人道主义援助和建筑材料在前往俄罗斯联邦新组成实体——顿涅茨克和卢甘斯克人民共和国的途中快速移动，以及扎波罗热和赫尔松地区，”普京说。 </div><div class="article__quote-info"><div class="elem-info"><div class="elem-info__share"><div class="share" data-id="1110643895" data-url="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230527/putin-says-border-guards-to-continue-protecting-russias-sovereignty-territorial-integrity-1110643895.html?share-block=1110643901" data-title="&quot;... it is vitally important to ensure fast movement of both military and civil vehicles and cargoes, including food, humanitarian aid, and construction materials on their way to new constituent entities of the Russian Federation – the Donetsk and Lugansk people’s republics, and the Zaporozhye and Kherson regions,&quot; Putin said. "></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">每年 5 月 28 日在俄罗斯庆祝边防卫队日。</div></div></div> ]]>;</description><pubDate> Sat, 27 May 2023 21:37:33 GMT</pubDate><guid ispermalink="false"> https://sputniknews.com/20230527/putin-says-border-guards-to-continue-protecting-russias-sovereignty-territorial-integrity-1110643895.html</guid><link/> https://sputniknews.com/20230527/putin-says-border-guards-to-continue-protecting-russias-sovereignty-territorial-integrity-1110643895.html<category>俄罗斯</category><category>弗拉基米尔普京</category><category>俄罗斯</category><category>俄罗斯边防局</category><category>边界</category><category>边境管制</category></item><item><title><![CDATA[Texas House of Reps. Launches State's AG Ken Paxton's Impeachment Proceedings]]></title><description><![CDATA[<div class="article__header"><div class="article__announce"><div class="media" data-media-tipe="ar16x9"><div class="media__size"><div class="photoview__open" data-photoview-group="1110643690" data-photoview-src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e5/03/0b/1082310789_0:0:3072:2048_1440x900_80_0_1_0e0d57cfcfc6851511a3d08adccaad22.jpg?source-sid=ap_photo" data-photoview-image-id="1082310787" data-photoview-sharelink="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230527/texas-house-of-reps-launches-states-ag-ken-paxtons-impeachment-proceedings-1110643690.html?share-img=1082310787"><noindex><div class="photoview__open-info"> <span class="photoview__copyright">© AP Photo / <a href="http://www.apimages.com/metadata/Index/Google-Texas-Lawsuit/24c92c8d08d3406dba1096d7141a5c95/6/0" title="托尼·古铁雷斯">Tony Gutierrez</a></span><span class="photoview__desc-text">在这张 2020 年 6 月 28 日的档案照片中，得克萨斯州总检察长肯·帕克斯顿 (Ken Paxton) 在达拉斯 Love Field 机场等待副总统迈克·彭斯 (Mike Pence) 抵达。帕克斯顿的高级员工因被指控贿赂他们的前任老板而大规模外逃，这使得共和党人寻求 4300 万美元的公共资金，以用外部律师取代其中的一些人，以领导针对谷歌的高调反托拉斯诉讼。</span> </div></noindex><img media-type="ar16x9" data-source-sid="ap_photo" alt="In this June 28, 2020 file photo, Texas' Attorney General Ken Paxton waits on the flight line for the arrival of Vice President Mike Pence at Love Field in Dallas. The mass exodus of Paxton's top staff over accusations of bribery against their former boss has left the Republicans seeking $43 million in public funds to replace some of them with outside lawyers to lead a high-profile antitrust lawsuit against Google. - Sputnik International, 1920, 27.05.2023" title="在这张 2020 年 6 月 28 日的档案照片中，得克萨斯州总检察长肯·帕克斯顿 (Ken Paxton) 在达拉斯 Love Field 机场等待副总统迈克·彭斯 (Mike Pence) 抵达。帕克斯顿的高级员工因被指控贿赂他们的前任老板而大规模外逃，这使得共和党人寻求 4300 万美元的公共资金，以用外部律师取代其中的一些人，以领导针对谷歌的高调反托拉斯诉讼。" src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e5/03/0b/1082310789_0:0:3072:1728_1920x0_80_0_0_e39bbf68cd396f4f9c12fd3503ee347b.jpg" decoding="async" width="1920" height="1080" srcset="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e5/03/0b/1082310789_0:0:3072:1728_640x0_80_0_0_8dd09699dcf2cce35872bb3c648fbac2.jpg 640w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e5/03/0b/1082310789_0:0:3072:1728_1280x0_80_0_0_5cc53629fa0166eed4d22f2926ec0ba4.jpg 1280w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e5/03/0b/1082310789_0:0:3072:1728_1920x0_80_0_0_e39bbf68cd396f4f9c12fd3503ee347b.jpg 1920w" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div></div><div class="media__copyright " data-nosnippet=""><div class="media__copyright-item m-copyright"> © 美联社照片 / <a href="http://www.apimages.com/metadata/Index/Google-Texas-Lawsuit/24c92c8d08d3406dba1096d7141a5c95/6/0" title="托尼·古铁雷斯">托尼古铁雷斯</a></div></div></div></div><div class="article__messengers"><div class="flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label"></span></div><div class="flex-align_center"></div><div class="article__telegram-news flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label">订阅</span></div><div class="flex-align_center"><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/SputnikInt" title="国际的" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">国际的</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://telegram.me/sputniknewsindia" title="印度" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">印度</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/sputnik_africa" title="非洲" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">非洲</a></div></div></div><div class="article__author"><div class="article__author-item"><div class="article__author-wrapper"><div class="article__author-info"><div class="article__author-name">叶戈尔·沙波瓦洛夫</div><div class="article__author-links"><a class="m-color-main" href="https://sputniknews.com/author_shapovalov_egor/" title="所有材料">所有材料</a><a data-modal-open="feedback_author" href="mailto:e.shapovalov@sputniknews.com" title="写给作者">写给作者</a></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__announce-text">得克萨斯州共和党总检察长肯·帕克斯顿正面临该州众议院发起的前所未有的弹劾程序。这位饱受贿赂、滥用公众信任和无能指控困扰的丑闻缠身的律师呼吁他的支持者和平抗议可能导致他被免职的投票。 </div></div><div class="article__body"><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">众议院召开会议，就弹劾和停职 60 岁的帕克斯顿展开辩论。针对他的指控一直困扰着他作为德克萨斯州顶级律师的三个任期。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">程序包括建议弹劾他的调查委员会的开场陈述，随后是四个小时的辩论和投票前的总结发言。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">帕克斯顿将弹劾程序视为“政治戏剧”，并鼓励他的支持者在国会大厦和平地发表意见。 </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="quote"><div class="article__quote"><div class="article__quote-text">帕克斯顿说：“他们表现出对选举过程的绝对蔑视。支持这种欺骗性弹劾企图的每一位政治家都会对德克萨斯众议院的信誉造成持久损害。” </div><div class="article__quote-info"><div class="elem-info"><div class="elem-info__share"><div class="share" data-id="1110643690" data-url="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230527/texas-house-of-reps-launches-states-ag-ken-paxtons-impeachment-proceedings-1110643690.html?share-block=1110643694" data-title="&quot;They are showcasing their absolute contempt for the electoral process. Every politician who supports this deceitful impeachment attempt will inflict lasting damage on the credibility of the Texas House,&quot; said Paxton."></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">这位司法部长多年来一直受到联邦调查局的调查，指控他滥用职权协助捐赠者。 2015 年，他还因证券欺诈罪被起诉，但尚未受审。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">帕克斯顿在 2020 年要求美国最高法院<a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20201209/seventeen-us-states-back-texas-bid-to-overturn-biden-election-1081412109.html" target="_blank">推翻</a>乔·拜登总统对唐纳德·特朗普的选举胜利时，引起了全国的关注。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">如果被弹劾，帕克斯顿将被免职并接受参议院审判。得克萨斯州共和党州长格雷格·阿博特随后将任命临时替代人选。最终免职需要参议院三分之二的票数，其中一名参议员是帕克斯顿的妻子安吉拉。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">帕克斯顿的批评者认为，这种指责早就应该发生了。过去，他承认违反了德克萨斯州的证券法，并面临与一家科技初创公司有关的证券欺诈指控。他还接受了与有争议的情况有关的个人的大笔捐款，其中包括一名高管，其公司正在接受医疗补助欺诈调查。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">然而，帕克斯顿与奥斯汀房地产开发商内特保罗的关系似乎引发了弹劾程序。帕克斯顿的八名高级助手告知联邦调查局，他们担心他滥用职权帮助保罗就 2 亿美元的财产阴谋提出未经证实的指控。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">在弹劾指控中，有一项指控称帕克斯顿参与了止赎诉讼并发表了有利于保罗的法律意见。此外，贿赂指控称，保罗雇用这名妇女以换取法律援助，并资助对帕克斯顿的家进行昂贵的装修。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">帕克斯顿办公室的高级律师克里斯希尔顿表示，司法部长亲自支付了所有维修和翻新费用。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">这些事态发展可能导致共和党最著名的法律人物之一迅速垮台，此外，在德克萨斯州近 200 年的历史中，只有两名官员被弹劾。</div></div></div> ]]>;</description><pubDate> Sat, 27 May 2023 21:22:08 GMT</pubDate><guid ispermalink="false"> https://sputniknews.com/20230527/texas-house-of-reps-launches-states-ag-ken-paxtons-impeachment-proceedings-1110643690.html</guid><link/> https://sputniknews.com/20230527/texas-house-of-reps-launches-states-ag-ken-paxtons-impeachment-proceedings-1110643690.html<category>美洲</category><category>我们</category><category>得克萨斯州</category><category>共和党</category><category>肯帕克斯顿</category><category>唐纳德·特朗普</category><category>欺诈罪</category><category>弹劾</category></item></channel></rss>